                    <h1 class="txt-black">Entry Criteria, Rules and Judging Process </h1>
                    <p class="text-center sub-intro-head txt-gold">Entries open on Monday 30th March and Close on Friday 1st May 2015 at 17:00hrs.</p>
                    <p>The Maverick Awards, its organisers, partners and sponsors as well it's judges pride themselves with maintaining a high level of integrity and credibility of its assessments, in this regard all entries MUST adhere to the minimum entry criteria and rules as stipulated or risk automatic disqualification. It is also imperative that entrants supply the judges with accurate and precise information in order for the adjudication to function seamlessly.</p>
