                <h2 class="txt-black">Minimum Entry Criteria</h2>
                <p>Age of Entrepreneurs: 18 - 34 years, and not older by 31st June 2015.</p>
                <p>Turnover: Minimum of R3million revenue per annum - Except in the case of The Maverick Start-Up of The Year Award where a business's revenue MUST range between R1million and R3 million in annual revenue.</p>
                <p>Business Age: 3 years or more - Except in the case of The Maverick Start-Up of The Year Award that MUST be at least 1 year old and less than 3 years in operation.</p>
                <p>Employees: Minimum of 3 full-time employees with employment contracts in place.</p>
                <p>Clients: Minimum of 3 verifiable clients that you service.</p>
                <p>Suppliers: Minimum of 3 verifiable suppliers that service your business.</p>
                <p>Who Can Enter: Any owner, partner or management team member of the enterprise can enter directly by filling the entry form or third parties can nominate a young deserving and qualifying entrepreneur(s) that meets the criteria.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="bg-gold back-box">
