                <h2 class="txt-white">Rules of Entry</h2>
                <p class="txt-white">Entrepreneurs must be owners of businesses that are formally registered and primarily operate within South Africa.</p>
                <p class="txt-white">The enterprise in question MUST be at least 50% owned and controlled by a shareholder(s) under the age of 35.</p>
                <p class="txt-white">Entrepreneurs must be the registered owners and operators of their enterprises.</p>
                <p class="txt-white">Entrepreneurs must comply with the legislation of South Africa, therefore they must be in possession of Tax Clearance Certificates, BEE Certificates and have Audited Financial Statements, Management Accounts and a Bank Account.</p>
                <p class="txt-white">All entrants, finalists and winners consent to the usage of their names, images and company names in media and other communications related to The Maverick Awards either by Under 35 Mavericks or any of our partners and sponsors.</p>
            </div>
